    • Method Detail

      • confirm

        @UiThread
 @NonNull
public GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.PromptResponse confirm(@NonNull
                                                                              LoginStorage.LoginEntry login)
        Confirm the prompt by responding with a LoginStorage.LoginEntry. For GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.LoginStoragePrompt.Type.SAVE, confirm with the entry to be saved. This can be the original entry as provided by logins[0] or a modified entry based on that. Confirming a GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.LoginStoragePrompt.Type.SAVE prompt request triggers a LoginStorage.Delegate.onLoginSave(org.mozilla.geckoview.LoginStorage.LoginEntry) request in the runtime delegate with the confirmed login entry.
        Parameters:
        login - A LoginStorage.LoginEntry specifying the login entry saved.
        Returns:
        A GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.PromptResponse which can be used to complete the GeckoResult associated with this prompt.
